pull.title: Docs: Enable TLS in link to chris.beams.io
pull.body: This PR enables TLS in a documentation link to chris.beams.io, which improves security.  This change was originally part of https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/13778 , which was closed for reasons unrelated to this change.
